&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possessing the ability to understand schematics and technical manuals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be reliable and have excellent communication skills, both oral and written.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be willing to submit to pre-employment screening, including criminal background check and drug screen.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic computer knowledge is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be 18 years of age or older.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-4 years of electrical apprenticeship preferred&lt;/li&gt;
