&lt;p&gt;The project is for the &lt;strong&gt;United States Army Corps of Engineers&lt;/strong&gt; and will require a background check to gain site access. &lt;strong&gt;Davis-Bacon wages will be paid.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
