&lt;li&gt;Produce schedules and monitor attendance of crew.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allocate general and daily responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise and train workers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure labor and resources are adequate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guarantee all safety precautions and quality standards are followed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise the use of machinery and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor expenditure and ensure it remains within budget.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resolve problems when they arise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report progress to managers, engineers etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
